title: The title of hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options", now it changes with settings.
OB: When reopening the hyperlink builder, the title changes to "www.actuate.com" instead of "Hyperlink Options".
EB: The title of hyperlink builder should always be "Hyperlink Options", regardless of settings.
SR:
Steps to reproduce: 
1. Open the hyperlink builder. 
2. Click on "OK". 
3. Close the hyperlink builder. 
4. Reopen the hyperlink builder. 

Expected result: The title of the hyperlink builder should be "Hyperlink Options".
